at never turned into preserved artifacts.\n\nNext steps:\n1. Fix or trim the failing native tests under `tests/src/ch.qos.reload4j/reload4j/1.2.19`, especially the `Log4jEntityResolver`, `EnhancedThrowableRenderer`, and Chainsaw/AWT paths, then rerun `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=ch.qos.reload4j:reload4j:1.2.19`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew generateMetadata -Pcoordinates=ch.qos.reload4j:reload4j:1.2.19` in an environment where `native-image-agent` is available on the library path.\n3. Commit the resulting `tests/src/ch.qos.reload4j/reload4j/1.2.19` and `metadata/ch.qos.reload4j/reload4j/1.2.19` changes to the preserved branch once both steps pass."}}
